<html><head><title>Weekly Exclusive Omens Alternate Advancement Ability</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Weekly Exclusive Omens Alternate Advancement Ability</h3><p>Today we have an exclusive Alternate Advancement Ability which Shamans can get in Omens of War.<blockquote><br><b>Shaman:</b><br><i>Spiritual Channeling</i> - While this ability is active, all of your spells will be fueled directly by the energy of your body, consuming hit points rather than mana.<br></blockquote><br>This is certainly one of the more interesting abilities so far...</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Thu 19 Aug 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#819<br>Printed On: Tue Aug 31 13:44:21 PDT 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>